# PHP tempnam() output (3-letter prefix + 18+ alnum chars). Pattern is strict
# enough not to match phpstan*.neon, phpunit.xml.dist, etc. (those have '.' or '-').
/php[A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9][A-Za-z0-9]*
